    Class Description
    Event

    Folder
    A folder contains multiple Items, which contain the tests themselves.
    Info
    Info object contains basic test collection information.
    Item
    An Item is essentially one request and it accompanying tests.
    Request
    A request specifies url and method to call.
    TestCollection
    Test collection configuration.
    Variable
    Variable entity that contains some predefined variable coming from the test collection json file.
